; Regression test for issue #779: pricedb --both-directions should emit
; entries in both forward and reverse directions.
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/779

P 2024/01/01 EUR 1.20 USD

2024/01/01 Test
    Assets:EUR   100 EUR @ 1.20 USD
    Assets:Cash   -120 USD

; Without --both-directions, only forward prices are shown
test pricedb
P 2024/01/01 00:00:00 EUR 1.20 USD
end test

; With --both-directions, both forward and reverse prices are shown
test pricedb --both-directions
P 2024/01/01 00:00:00 EUR 1.20 USD
P 2024/01/01 00:00:00 USD 0.83333333 EUR
end test
